#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.30"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.30:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Koṭigāmavagga"
msgstr "3. At the Village of Koṭi"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Gavampatisutta"
msgstr "30. With Gavampati"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: cetesu → cetīsu (bj) | cetiyesu (s1-3)
#. VAR: sahañcanike → sahajātiyaṃ (bj) | sahajaniye (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn56.30:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ sambahulā therā bhikkhū cetesu viharanti sahañcanike."
msgstr ""
"At one time several mendicants were staying in the land of the Cetis at "
"Sahajāti."

msgctxt "sn56.30:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sambahulānaṃ therānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ pacchābhattaṃ "
"piṇḍapātapaṭikkantānaṃ maṇḍalamāḷe sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ "
"ayamantarākathā udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"Now at that time, after the meal, on return from alms-round, several senior "
"mendicants sat together in the pavilion and this discussion came up among "
"them:"

msgctxt "sn56.30:1.3"
msgid ""
"“yo nu kho, āvuso, dukkhaṃ passati dukkhasamudayampi so passati, "
"dukkhanirodhampi passati, dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadampi passatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverends, does someone who sees suffering also see the origin of "
"suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the "
"cessation of suffering?”"

# read there
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.437"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: gavampati thero → gavampatitthero (s1-3, km) | gavampati there (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.30:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā gavampati thero bhikkhū etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When they said this, Venerable Gavampati said to those senior mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn56.30:2.2"
msgid "“sammukhā metaṃ, āvuso, bhagavato sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverends, I have heard and learned this in the presence of the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn56.30:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘yo, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ passati dukkhasamudayampi so passati, "
"dukkhanirodhampi passati, dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadampi passati."
msgstr ""
"‘Someone who sees suffering also sees the origin of suffering, the cessation "
"of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.30:2.4"
msgid ""
"Yo dukkhasamudayaṃ passati dukkhampi so passati, dukkhanirodhampi passati, "
"dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadampi passati."
msgstr ""
"Someone who sees the origin of suffering also sees suffering, the cessation "
"of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.30:2.5"
msgid ""
"Yo dukkhanirodhaṃ passati dukkhampi so passati, dukkhasamudayampi passati, "
"dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadampi passati."
msgstr ""
"Someone who sees the cessation of suffering also sees suffering, the origin "
"of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.30:2.6"
msgid ""
"Yo dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ passati dukkhampi so passati, "
"dukkhasamudayampi passati, dukkhanirodhampi passatī’”ti."
msgstr ""
"Someone who sees the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering also "
"sees suffering, the origin of suffering, and the cessation of suffering.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.30:2.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.30:2.8"
msgid "Koṭigāmavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.30:3.1"
msgid "Dve vajjī sammāsambuddho,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.30:3.2"
msgid "arahaṃ āsavakkhayo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.30:3.3"
msgid "Mittaṃ tathā ca loko ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn56.30:3.4"
msgid "pariññeyyaṃ gavampatīti."
msgstr ""
